# Code Owners for paths that publish to S3.
#
# This file auto-requests reviewers on PRs that touch the listed paths. To
# ENFORCE that the listed reviewer must approve before merge (vs just being
# tagged), enable a branch protection rule in the GitHub UI:
#   Settings → Branches → main → "Require pull request reviews" + "Require
#   review from Code Owners".
#
# The branch-per-env publish workflow means a merge to main triggers a publish
# to prod S3 — same with merges to dev/qa. CODEOWNERS guards prod by gating
# merges to main; we deliberately don't gate dev/qa to keep iteration fast.

# Anything that produces what gets shipped to candidates.
experiments/                                @Collin-GP
scripts/python/publish_experiments.py       @Collin-GP
scripts/python/test_publish_experiments.py  @Collin-GP
scripts/python/test_experiment_manifests.py @Collin-GP
.github/workflows/publish-experiments.yml   @Collin-GP
.github/CODEOWNERS                          @Collin-GP
